-- Comcast’s NBC Extends French Open Partnership Through 2024
-- B y   D a n   H a r t
-- 2012-08-05T13:02:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-05/comcast-s-nbc-extends-french-open-partnership-through-2024.html
Comcast’s NBC Sports extended its
partnership with the French Tennis Federation to cover the
French Open tennis championship through 2024, the company said.  Terms of the agreement weren’t disclosed. The network will
air the opening Sunday, the middle weekend, as well as the men’s
and women’s semifinals and finals, NBC Sports said in an e-
mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Hart at 
 dahart@bloomberg.net  